he Elves]], in which their name can be found in-game by searching the desk by the [[Elven Crystal Chest]] in the [[Tower of Voices]]. In addition, they were sent an engraved crystal decoration in real life to commemorate the quest.\n\n{{Grand Library}}\n[[Category:Texts and tomes]]"}